  "industry_note": "UNS N06625 / EN 2.4856 / NiCr22Mo9Nb / Alloy 625 — Ni-base solid-solution-strengthened superalloy (Ni ≥58, Cr 20-23, Mo 8-10, Fe ≤5, Nb+Ta 3.15-4.15). Solution-strengthened (no aging required). 우수한 oxidation 저항 1100°C + chloride pitting/SCC 저항. AM LPBF 해수 환경 valve / piping (FPSO topside), aerospace afterburner liner, nuclear reactor 부품, AM LPBF 의 standard nickel superalloy.",
